rengarenga
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:also called renga lily, rock lily a drooping-leaved lily with branching flower-stems, found in open rocky situations from Cook Strait northwards
Origin: Maori
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes:
